name: are u okay ?
description:
500 twitter follower celebration :


We live with a lot of heads, heart, and souls with our own way of survival.  I just don't know what you or others feel or even struggle with.

everyone asks "how are you?", that's really oke but if no one asks if you're ok, just pick some meds :

- food
- stay in bed
- affection
- laugh
- cry
- read book
- work
- sing
- playing music
- sleep
- love other
- draw
- watching movie
- vacation 
- help & support other
- respect other
- anything you want to pick for your health ヾ(˙❥˙)ﾉ

everything's matters ♥️

artworks : smile (stable for feeling)
flower (value our self)
star (shine our mind ) 

song : trace time & life goes on - Lucy enigma
